Description_lang: Skeinspinner Takazj launches explosive webs at players, inflicting $s1 Nature damage to all players within $A1 yards. If more than one player is in the area, they are bound together with $@spellname440001, slowing movement by $440001s2%. If bound players move more than $439992s2 yards apart or if Anub'arash charges through the webs, they will break and remove $@spellname440001.
